# The repository is LF end to end, on every platform.
#
# .githooks/commit-msg is executed by bash on Windows as well as POSIX, and a
# CRLF shebang is not executable — the hook would fail to run on a fresh clone
# under the default Windows core.autocrlf=true, silently removing one of the
# three attribution layers (P0 §4.2) on a platform P0 §5.2 treats as supported
# rather than assumed.
* text=auto eol=lf
